    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Volusio Basso Cereali <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> legato totius <lb n="3"/>innocentiae et <lb n="4"/>aequitatis et consi<lb break="no" n="5"/>milis moderatio<lb break="no" n="6"/>nis viro <lb n="7"/>Lepcimagnenses ex de<lb break="no" n="8"/>creto ordinis mu<lb break="no" n="9"/>nicipi et patrono perpetuo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is carved over an erased earlier text (of which traces remain). (B): AE 1982: Z. 8-9: mu/nicipi patrono. Z. 8-9: mu/nicipi et in ligature.</p>
            </div>
